name: Sci Fi Boudoir
description:
Title: Sci Fi Boudoir
Location: Salem, Oregon
Year Taken: 2020
About this photo: Celeste first came to my studio to model a boudoir Geralt of Rivia with my new studio sword. That meeting turned into a business relationship where she did hair and makeup work for me with my clients. This particular set happened after a boudoir photo session she’d worked on for me. She wanted to do a cosplay boudoir set featuring her Guardians of the Galaxy character, Starlord. The concept was to start with a more traditional boudoir and move into a fully clothed and realized gender bender character. We were about halfway into her costume at this point, you can even see a little bit of the headboard in this image.
